info.text: Federal regulations require you to have $2,000 in your Robinhood brokerage account and a suitable investment profile in order to use margin. Suitability is determined by asking you a few questions in the app about your investment experience, goals, and sensitivity to risk. You can enable margin while you’re on Gold by (1) increasing your account value to $2,000 by depositing funds and (2) updating your investment profile.
